This is likely on the liner New York on October 7 or 8, 1915, since Sir Johnston Forbes-Robertson and Lord Aberdeen (in neighboring photos) and Bayley all arrived on that voyage from Liverpool to New York.

See NYT of Oct 8, 1915 for a list of &quot;Passengers from Liverpool.&quot;
